{"about_the_game":"Take a cruise through different countries. Relax as you enjoy the views, and tourists take pictures of their favourite landmarks. Take it easy - or not so much! But most importantly: <strong>be careful</strong>.<br><br><strong><u>Features:</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use your <strong>mouse</strong> to drive with the <strong>on-screen controls</strong>.<br></li><li>Game driven by <strong>physics</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>15 handmade levels</strong> set on <strong>3 different countries</strong>.<br></li><li><strong>Beautiful music</strong> unique to each country.<br></li><li><strong>Scoring system</strong> (don't crash, take the photo and beat the time mark).<br></li><li><strong>World leaderboards</strong> to see who is the fastest captain.<br></li><li><strong>Twitch integration:</strong> join the cruise of your favorite streamer and cross your fingers that you won't die if the captain has to crash.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/Desc_title_02_en.png?t=1720815755\" /><br>You will be able to navigate through <strong>different countries</strong>, each with its own architectural style, environment and music. Close your eyes and feel like you are there, but not for too long or the consequences will be catastrophic.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/Desc_01.gif?t=1720815755\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/Desc_title_01_en.png?t=1720815755\" /><br>Drive the cruise with a <strong>virtual rudder</strong>, which will make you feel like you're driving a real cruise ship. In addition, physics feel like real physics! So... remember to brake in time, waters are treacherous...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/Desc_02.gif?t=1720815755\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/Desc_title_03_en.png?t=1720815755\" /><br>The important thing is to get there, no rush. Although... if you like <strong>challenges,</strong> you can <u>get rewards</u> if you manage to make the perfect journey in the shortest time possible.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/Desc_03.gif?t=1720815755\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/Desc_title_04_en.png?t=1720815755\" /><br>Take <strong>pictures</strong> of the landmarks unique to each level to go back home with a souvenir of your holiday.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/Desc_04.gif?t=1720815755\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/Desc_title_05_en.png?t=1720815755\" /><br>Currents, whirlpools and other <strong>obstacles</strong> will test your skills as a true cruise captain; let them sink in... but don't go too deep! You'll need them to avoid tricker sections!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2103480/extras/Desc_05.gif?t=1720815755\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First trip","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103480/90fdc583226a2a11a65b8de2858b8a8e54ecc5d6.jpg"},{"name":"3 stars","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103480/321b858bc6c2b1054dbad11057580f73670e5a2a.jpg"},{"name":"Greece","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2103480/60c06f03381e8db8ae7f40551cf067e213183dfe.jpg"},{"name":"Italy","path":"https://cdn.a